OL,6,FFootball fans at the FA Cup semi-final
OL,7,Fmatch between and Manchester United
OL,8,Fare being encouraged to clap in the
OL,9,F21st minute for a supporter who is in
OL,10,Fhospital on an urgent waiting list for
OL,11,Fa heart transplant.
OL,13,FLouis O'Brien-Smith, from , has
OL,14,Fdilated cardiomyopathy, which is
OL,15,Fbelieved to be caused by chemotherapy
OL,16,Fhe underwent for leukaemia. Louis had
OL,17,Fcancer twice as a child.
