OL,3,CCoventry supporters urged to clap for
OL,4,Cfan in hospital with heart failure
OL,6,F"My son has battled all of his life.
OL,7,FIt feels so unfair and so, so cruel.
OL,8,FThe situation right now feels so scary
OL,9,Fand I cannot bare the thought of
OL,10,Flosing him. If I can rally around
OL,11,Fsupport now to show Louis how we are
OL,12,Fall behind him then that is what I
OL,13,Fshall do!"
OL,15,FDespite being isolated in a hotel
OL,16,Froom, Louis' mum is keen to show him
OL,17,Fhe is not alone.
