OL,4,Cfan in hospital with heart failure
OL,6,F"For the supporters to clap for him on
OL,7,Fthe 21st minute will show him as he
OL,8,Fwatches away from home that he isn't
OL,9,Fforgotten," she said.
OL,11,F"To know that half of the city, his
OL,12,Fhome town are thinking of him and
OL,13,Facknowledging him means the world!"
OL,15,FThe hope and end goal for Louis and
OL,16,Fhis mum Chantelle is to raise
OL,17,Fawareness of his condition and organ
OL,18,Fdonation.
