OL,6,FThey've had the support of singer and
OL,7,Frapper YoungBloodRap, who produced a
OL,8,Fsong called 'Mr High (Louis Tribute)'
OL,9,Fthat tells Louis' story and mentions
OL,10,Fthe importance of donors.
OL,12,FAnd Louis has even amounted to a
OL,13,Fsocial media account following of over
OL,14,F60,000, much to the amazement of his
OL,15,Fmum. She said: "In the words of his
OL,16,FTikTok followers- he's waiting for a
OL,17,Fheart fit for a king!"
