OL,3,CCoventry supporters urged to clap for
OL,4,Cfan in hospital with heart failure
OL,6,FFrom a young age, Louis has always
OL,7,Fstruggled with his health. He had
OL,8,Fmeningitis at 11 weeks old and at 18
OL,9,Fmonths was diagnosed with acute
OL,10,Fmyeloid leukaemia, a rare and
OL,11,Faggressive form of cancer and he
OL,12,Fovercame it twice.
OL,14,FHowever, Louis went on to have
OL,15,Fcomplications from chemotherapy
OL,16,Fincluding damage to his bones, legs,
OL,17,Ftibia and hips, but also to his heart,
OL,18,Fleading to him being put on an urgent
OL,19,Fheart transplant waiting list.
