OL,6,FHis mum said that he's spent so long
OL,7,Fin and out of hospital treatment in
OL,8,FBirmingham, that he's got a bit of a
OL,9,FBrummie accent.
OL,11,FHe struggles to walk, and his main
OL,12,Fambition was to walk his dog before
OL,13,Flast Christmas, but because of the
OL,14,Fseverity of his multiple health
OL,15,Fconditions, he was not able to.
