OL,4,Cfan in hospital with heart failure
OL,6,FBut that won't stop him from carrying
OL,7,Fon fighting. Chantelle said: "I don't
OL,8,Fwant to wake up for the worst to
OL,9,Fhappen and wish I could have done
OL,10,Fmore. Louis is 21 now, he's living
OL,11,Fbreathing and fighting now.
OL,13,F"From his hospital bed, he raises the
OL,14,Fimportance and awareness of the need
OL,15,Ffor organ donation."
