OL,6,F"He's spent so much time fighting he
OL,7,Fhasn't had the chance to do all the
OL,8,Fthings young people do. And for him
OL,9,Fnow to sit and wait and remain in the
OL,10,Fhospital just feels so cruel.
OL,11,FParticularly after last week's stand
OL,12,Fdown."
OL,14,F"He's so young, so deserving of a
OL,15,Fchance at life."
